'''Daren Horley''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Amphi-Hydrus]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the 16 years and older category. He was 29 at the time his entry was published.<ref name="DAA">{{GalaxyCite|7|Design An Alien}}</ref>

